{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sloths are complex creatures that require careful creation and a suitable habitat. After creating a sloth, you’re responsible for feeding them, providing fulfilling activities, and giving them opportunities to exercise and rest."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Every sloth has a "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/name"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/color-swift.property"},{"type":"text","text":". You can optionally provide a "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/power-swift.property"},{"type":"text","text":" if your sloth has special supernatural abilities."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"slothPower.png"}]},{"anchor":"Create-a-Sloth","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Create a Sloth"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To create a standard sloth without any special supernatural powers, you initialize a new instance of the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth"},{"type":"text","text":" structure, and supply a name and a color, as the following code shows:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["var sloth = Sloth(name: \"Super Sloth\", color: .blue, power: .none)"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If your sloth possesses one of the special powers of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ice"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"fire"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"wind"},{"type":"text","text":", or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"lightning"},{"type":"text","text":", you can specify this at creation:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["var superSloth = Sloth(name: \"Silly Sloth\", color: .green, power: .lightning)"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you’re creating a large number of sloths, you can define your own random name generator that conforms to the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/NameGenerator"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol, and use it to generate names:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["let slothNamer = MyCustomSlothNamer()","var sloths: [Sloth] = []","","for _ in 0...100 {","    let name = slothNamer.generateName(seed: 0)","    var sloth = Sloth(name: name, color: .green, power: .ice)","    ","    sloths.append(sloth)","}"]},{"anchor":"Provide-a-Habitat","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Provide a Habitat"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sloths thrive in comfortable habitats. To create a sloth-friendly habitat, you specify whether it’s humid, warm, or both. The following listing creates a habitat that’s humid and warm, which results in a high "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Habitat\/comfortLevel"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["let lovelyHabitat = Habitat(isHumid: true, isWarm: true)"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"After you create a sloth habitat, you’re ready for sloths to sleep in it. Sleeping in a habitat increases the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/energyLevel"},{"type":"text","text":" of the sloth by the comfort level of the habitat. Sloths sleep for long periods so, by default, your sloth sleeps for 12 hours, but you can also customize this value:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["superSloth.sleep(in: lovelyHabitat)","hyperSloth.sleep(in: lovelyHabitat, for: 2)"]},{"anchor":"Exercise-a-Sloth","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Exercise a Sloth"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To keep your sloths happy and fulfilled, you can create activities for them to perform. Define your activities by conforming to the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol and implementing the "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity\/perform(with:)"},{"type":"text","text":" method:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct Sightseeing: Activity {","    func perform(with sloth: inout Sloth) -> Speed {","        sloth.energyLevel -= 10","        return .slow","    }","}"]},{"anchor":"Feed-a-Sloth","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Feed a Sloth"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Sloths require sustenance to perform activities, so you can feed them "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/Food"},{"type":"text","text":". Standard sloth food includes leaves and twigs:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["superSloth.eat(.largeLeaf)","hyperSloth.eat(.twig)"]},{"anchor":"Schedule-Care-for-a-Sloth","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Schedule Care for a Sloth"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To make it easy to care for your sloth, SlothCreator provides a "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/CareSchedule"},{"type":"text","text":" structure that lets you define activities or foods for your sloth to enjoy at specific times. Create the schedule, then provide a tuple of a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Date"},{"type":"text","text":" and an "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity"},{"type":"text","text":", or you can use some of the standard care procedures:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["let events: [(Date, CareSchedule.Event)] = [","    (Date.now, .bedtime),","    (Date(timeIntervalSinceNow: 12*60*60), .breakfast),","    (Date(timeIntervalSinceNow: 13*60*60), .activity(Sightseeing()))","]","","let schedule = CareSchedule(events: events)","superSloth.schedule = schedule"]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/slothcreator\/gettingstarted"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/GettingStarted","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Create a sloth and assign personality traits and abilities."}],"kind":"article","metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","title":"Getting Started with Sloths","role":"article","modules":[{"name":"SlothCreator"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator"]]},"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Essentials","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/tutorials\/SlothCreator","doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth"],"generated":true}],"references":{"doc://SlothCreator/documentation/SlothCreator/NameGenerator":{"role":"symbol","title":"NameGenerator","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"NameGenerator"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A type that generates names for sloths."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/NameGenerator","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"NameGenerator"}],"url":"\/documentation\/slothcreator\/namegenerator"},"doc://SlothCreator/documentation/SlothCreator/Activity":{"role":"symbol","title":"Activity","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Activity"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A type that declares an activity a Sloth can perform."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Activity","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"Activity"}],"url":"\/documentation\/slothcreator\/activity"},"doc://SlothCreator/documentation/SlothCreator/Sloth/color-swift.property":{"role":"symbol","title":"color","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"color"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Color","preciseIdentifier":"s:12SlothCreator0A0V5ColorO"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The color of the sloth."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth\/color-swift.property","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/slothcreator\/sloth\/color-swift.property"},"slothPower.png":{"alt":"A diagram with the five sloth power types: ice, fire, wind, lightning, and none.","type":"image","identifier":"slothPower.png","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/slothPower@2x.png","traits":["2x","light"]},{"url":"\/images\/slothPower~dark@2x.png","traits":["2x","dark"]}]},"doc://SlothCreator/documentation/SlothCreator/Sloth":{"role":"symbol","title":"Sloth","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Sloth"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A model representing a sloth."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SlothCreator\/documentation\/SlothCreator\/Sloth","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"Sloth"}],"url":"\/documentation\/slothcreator\/sloth"},"doc://SlothCreator/documentation/SlothCreator/Activity/perform(with:)":{"role":"symbol","title":"perform(with:)","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","